OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FNew rules for household waste and
OL,7,Frecycling have come into force across
OL,8,FEngland.
OL,10,FStarting from Tuesday, households will
OL,11,Fnow separate their waste into three or
OL,12,Ffour different bins for waste
OL,13,Fcollectors to pick up, depending on
OL,14,Fthe area they live in.
OL,16,FThe government say the new rules will
OL,17,Fhelp simplify household waste
OL,18,Fcollections across the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
