OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FBut what do these new rules mean, and
OL,7,Fwho is affected by them? ITV News
OL,8,Fexplains.
OL,10,FWhat are the new rules?
OL,12,FThe new rules have come into effect as
OL,13,Fpart of government efforts to
OL,14,Fstandardise waste collection across
OL,15,FEngland's local authorities.
OL,17,FPrevious rules saw local councils
OL,18,Fdetermine their own systems, such as
OL,19,Fbin types and materials collected,
OL,20,Fleading to a confusing patchwork of
OL,21,Fsystems in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
