OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774995068
OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FAll households will now be required to
OL,7,Fseparate their waste into a maximum of
OL,8,Ffour different bins for waste
OL,9,Fcollectors to pick up.
OL,11,FAccording to Defra, waste collectors
OL,12,Fmust collect the following types of
OL,13,Fwaste separately:
OL,15,FUnder certain circumstances, paper and
OL,16,Fcard can be collected with other dry
OL,17,Frecyclable materials, meaning
OL,18,Fhouseholds in some areas will be able
OL,19,Fto separate their waste into three
OL,20,Fbins instead of four.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
