OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FMinisters say this will provide
OL,7,Fdifferent local authorities with the
OL,8,Fflexibility to deliver services that
OL,9,Fwork best for their communities.
OL,11,FCircular Economy Minister Mary Creagh
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are ending the bin
OL,13,Fcollections postcode lottery and
OL,14,Fmaking it easier for people to recycle
OL,15,Fwherever they live."
OL,17,FWhat is happening with food waste?
OL,19,FThe new rules will require councils to
OL,20,Fcollect food waste weekly and free of
OL,21,Fcharge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
