OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FTwo separate bins should be provided
OL,7,Fto each household - one small bin for
OL,8,Fthe kitchen (often called a caddy),
OL,9,Fand a larger bin for outside (for
OL,10,Fcollection).
OL,12,FWhen recycled separately, food waste
OL,13,Fcan be used to produce electricity, or
OL,14,Fas fertiliser.
OL,16,FClaire Shrewsbury, Director Insights
OL,17,Fand Innovation at climate action NGO
OL,18,FWrap said: "Food waste is where we'll
OL,19,Fsee the big win.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
