OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,F"It's difficult to prevent all food
OL,7,Fwaste, and so recycling one kitchen
OL,8,Fcaddy of unavoidable food waste could
OL,9,Fpower your fridge for 18 hours."
OL,11,FMore than #78 billion has been made
OL,12,Favailable to councils in England this
OL,13,Fyear, which includes funding for
OL,14,Fcouncils to roll out weekly food waste
OL,15,Fcollections for all households.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
