OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FWhy is the government making the
OL,7,Fchanges?
OL,9,FThe changes by the government come as
OL,10,Fa part of wider efforts to boost the
OL,11,Fso-called circular economy in the UK,
OL,12,Fso that resources are kept in use for
OL,13,Flonger, waste is reduced, and green
OL,14,Fgrowth is supported through investment
OL,15,Fin infrastructure and jobs.
OL,17,FThe government has also introduced an
OL,18,Fextended producer responsibility
OL,19,Fscheme, which sees packaging producers
OL,20,Fpay fees to cover the cost of
OL,21,Frecycling or waste management.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
