OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FIt also plans to launch the delayed
OL,7,Fdeposit return scheme in 2027, where
OL,8,Fconsumers pay a small deposit when
OL,9,Fbuying drinks in plastic bottles or
OL,10,Fmetal cans, which is returned upon
OL,11,Ftaking the empty container back to
OL,12,Fretailers.
OL,14,FWhen do these changes come into effect?
OL,16,FThe changes come into force on Tuesday
OL,17,FMarch 31.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
