OL,3,CNew recycling rules come into force
OL,4,Cacross England - what is changing?
OL,6,FHowever, for some local authorities
OL,7,Fwith area-specific delivery
OL,8,Fchallenges, the government has agreed
OL,9,Fadditional support will be provided,
OL,10,Fsuch as transitional arrangements
OL,11,Fallowing a later implementation date.
OL,13,FHouseholds can find out how their
OL,14,Fcouncil is rolling out the new rules
OL,15,Fat gov.uk/recycling-collections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
